        "Yu S, Ren K, Lou W. Attribute-based content distribution with hidden policy. In: 4th workshop on secure network protocols,2008. NPSec 2008; 2008. p. 39 e44. Thouraya Bouabana -Tebibel received a Ph.D. in Computer Science from USTHB University (Algeria) in collaboration with Pierre&Marie Curie University (France) in 2007. She has been an engineer/researcher for eight years and is now a full professor of computer science at Ecole Nationale Sup /C19erieure d 'Informatique in Algeria. She also is a researcher director at Laboratoire de Communication dans les Syst /C18emes Informatiques. She has successfully conducted numerous research projects and supervised BS, MS, and PhD theses. She has over 80 refereed publications anda book edited by Editions Universitaires Europ /C19eennes. Her research interests include formal methods, network security and information reuse and integration."
